{
  "stem": "22582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after a few weeks, after my friend was feeling better, we went to Bayreuth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where we were staying after the war for-- for about a year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, we had only 13 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then people started to come in, come in, come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish chaplain, and he-- he-- rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sort of organized a [NON-ENGLISH] for the people who are-- who were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, everybody was looking for somebody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody thought that he was the only one who survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And eventually, there were about 300 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they thought they were the [NON-ENGLISH] and-- no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was one of the five who was elected to be as a representative of the Jewish people in Bayreuth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we were getting some packages from UNRRA and that's-- that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a lot of people were getting married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They found each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were going to the weddings every week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And then I-- I got-- when I was in the hospital in Weiden, I met some-- some soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I asked them if they can-- I didn't remember the others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I knew that I have a brother in the United States, and he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- but I-- the last others I remember, he was in the Bronx somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But meanwhile, he was in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was in Europe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was in Italy at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my-- and then I told him that I have a uncles in Staten Island.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I gave them the name of my brother, I believe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Somehow they-- they got-- there was another story.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
